---
// The Studio section — brand story
---

<section id="studio" class="studio">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="studio-header">
      <p class="sec-index reveal">01 — The Studio</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title studio-title reveal reveal-delay-1">
        Born from<br />
        <em>Polish soil.</em><br />
        Built for the world.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Main grid -->
    <div class="studio-grid">
      <!-- Left: Story text -->
      <div class="studio-story">
        <div class="studio-story-block reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <p class="body-lg studio-lead">
            TARAXA is the engineering face of GUMEX — a Polish rubber
            manufacturer that has been running continuous production since <strong
              >1988</strong
            >. What began as a regional supplier evolved into a precision
            engineering house trusted by automotive, rail, and industrial
            clients across four continents.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="studio-story-block reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <p class="body-lg">
            The name <strong>TARAXA</strong> derives from <em>Taraxacum</em> — the
            scientific name of the dandelion, one of the few plants on Earth that
            naturally produces latex. For us, it is not just a name: it is a philosophy.
            The dandelion spreads with precision and purpose, adapts to any terrain,
            and persists where others cannot. So does our rubber.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="studio-story-block reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <p class="body-lg">
            Operating from our EU-certified facility in Poland, we combine
            decades of compound expertise with modern tooling capabilities —
            delivering custom rubber solutions that meet the most demanding
            engineering specifications.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Key facts -->
        <div class="studio-facts reveal reveal-delay-5" data-stagger>
          <div class="studio-fact reveal">
            <span class="studio-fact-icon">
              <svg
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                ><path
                  d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </span>
            <div>
              <strong>EU-Based Manufacturing</strong>
              <p class="body-sm">
                All production takes place in Poland under strict EU quality
                standards and environmental regulations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="studio-fact reveal">
            <span class="studio-fact-icon">
              <svg
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </span>
            <div>
              <strong>Short Lead Times</strong>
              <p class="body-sm">
                Prototypes in days, production runs in weeks — not the months
                typical of Asian sourcing chains.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="studio-fact reveal">
            <span class="studio-fact-icon">
              <svg
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                ><path
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </span>
            <div>
              <strong>ISO 9001 Certified</strong>
              <p class="body-sm">
                Full quality management system ensuring consistency from first
                prototype to mass production.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Visual column -->
      <div class="studio-visual">
        <div class="studio-img-main reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <img
            src="/images/AdobeStock_476218979.jpeg"
            alt="GUMEX rubber manufacturing facility in Poland"
