            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="studio-etymology-text">
            <p
              class="mono"
              style="color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;"
            >
              ETYMOLOGY
            </p>
            <p class="studio-etymology-word"><em>Taraxacum</em></p>
            <p class="body-sm" style="color: var(--ink-60)">
              The dandelion — one of Earth's few natural latex-producing plants.
              A symbol of resilience, precision distribution, and organic
